# Teacher Comments API Tests
# Note: These require authentication tokens

### Get comments for a student
GET {{Pusula.Api_HostAddress}}/api/teachercomments/student/{studentId}
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Get my students (Teacher only)
GET {{Pusula.Api_HostAddress}}/api/teachercomments/my-students
Authorization: Bearer {token}

### Create a new comment (Teacher only)
POST {{Pusula.Api_HostAddress}}/api/teachercomments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {token}

{
  "studentId": "student-guid-here",
  "comment": "Great performance in the course!"
}

### Delete a comment (Teacher only)
DELETE {{Pusula.Api_HostAddress}}/api/teachercomments/{commentId}
Authorization: Bearer {token}

